# 4. Data Profiling Summary

The dataset was profiled to understand its structure, completeness, and business relevance.

The following areas were evaluated:

* Record completeness
* Column consistency
* Data types
* Value distributions
* Uniqueness
* Referential integrity
* Business rule compliance

